metadata.name: Imagine, or eyesmoke
metadata.description: Unpleasant images creep into my head, and sometimes frightening ones, as well as pleasant ones, sweet as honey; you can become the hero of your fantasies and illusions, real stories with unimagined people, or you can jump from one planet to another in this way. Closing our eyes, we are no longer afraid. We begin to breathe and listen to the world around us.
